    <p>I've been having fun for the last few weeks building an interactive data visualisation tool, <a href="https://www.deeson.co.uk/drupal8r"><strong>The Drupal8r</strong></a>, to show how the Drupal community is coming together to develop the next release, Drupal 8.</p>
        
    
  



    
        
